item.title: Cheerful Loving Couple Bakers Drinking Coffee
item.description: Doomsday device? Ah, now the ball’s in Farnsworth’s court! Wow! A superpowers drug you can just rub onto your skin? You’d think it would be something you’d have to freebase. Look, last night was a mistake. Take me to your leader! Would you censor the Venus de Venus just because you can see her spewers?
